        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for information [about sex ratios] received from bird-catchers.</p>
            <p>"Can you form any theory about all the many cases which you have given me and others which have been published, of when one pair is killed, another soon appearing?"</p>
            <p>Facts about gay-coloured caterpillars very satisfactory.</p>
            <p>Comments on Pangenesis.</p>
        </abstract>
